    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Note</h2>The store description is from an older version of the game and currently work in progress!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742870/extras/48235a6776f8d70fb0ff46e285244081.poster.avif?t=1726123206\" width=500 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742870/extras/48235a6776f8d70fb0ff46e285244081.webm?t=1726123206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742870/extras/48235a6776f8d70fb0ff46e285244081.mp4?t=1726123206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Defenses</h2>You are up for a bumpy ride. Equip your train with a selection of guns and upgrade modules. However, you will need to pick carefully as not each weapon is good for each enemy and you have limited space and resources.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742870/extras/1cc701132cf4876962eadbdd220f83b5.poster.avif?t=1726123206\" width=500 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742870/extras/1cc701132cf4876962eadbdd220f83b5.webm?t=1726123206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742870/extras/1cc701132cf4876962eadbdd220f83b5.mp4?t=1726123206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Transport Cargo</h2>You will have a chance to transport cargo for various remaining countries and not all cargo is the same! Pick their location carefully and make sure to put them in defensible locations. Earn money for each successful delivery!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Do a Fast Delivery</h2>Cargo is best served fast and hot. Budget your resources carefully to build extra engines on your train and go faster to earn more money and reputation.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Your Arsenal</h2>With your hard earned money upgrade and unlock new weapons and utilities. You can never have too many guns!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the Lands</h2>Do your deliveries in different landscapes, each with differing bonuses and difficulties.",
